1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,360
Ipan yeyi tonajli más sakin*,

2
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:12,600
onkatka sen tlanamiktilistli ipan on kalpan itoka Caná de Galilea.

3
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:15,320
Inanaj Jesús ompa nemiya.

4
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:20,920
Niman Jesús iuan inomachtijkauan* no okinnotskej ipan on tlanamiktilistli.

5
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:24,040
Ijkuak otlan vino ipan on iluitl,

6
00:00:24,040 --> 00:00:25,800
María okijlij Jesús:

7
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:28,440
—Xok kipiyaj vino.

8
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,120
Pero Jesús okijlij:

9
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:31,320
—Siuatl,

10
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:32,960
¿tline* tinechijlia nejua?

11
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:36,680
Hasta aman xe ajsi on tonajli para nikchiuas milagros.

12
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:41,680
Kemaj inanaj ijkin okinmijlij on yejuan ompa tekichiuayaj:

13
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:45,240
—Xchiuakan nochi tlen yejua mechijlis.

14
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:55,320
Ompa onkatkaj chikuasen kontin tlachijchijtin ikan tetl niman ipan sen kontli ueli kalakiya kanaj ochenta noso cien litros de atl.

15
00:00:55,320 --> 00:01:00,160
On hebreos* kitekitiltiayaj on atl para nomajtekiayaj,

16
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:03,920
niman ijkon nokauayaj chipajkej ixpan Dios.

17
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:06,160
Jesús okinmijlij on tekichijkej:

18
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:09,480
—Xkintemakan in kontin ikan atl.

19
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:12,080
Niman kuajli okintemiltijkej.

20
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:13,800
Niman kemaj Jesús okinmijlij:

21
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:20,280
—Aman xkixtikan achijtsin niman xkitkilikan on tlayekanketl ipan in iluitl.

22
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:22,480
Niman yejuamej ijki okichijkej.

23
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:27,280
On tlayekanketl ipan on iluitl xkimatiya kanon oualeu,

24
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:32,720
yej san yejuamej on tekitkej kimatstikatkaj yejuan okixtijkej on atl.

25
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:37,640
On tlayekanketl okimat on atl yejuan Jesús okikuep vino,

26
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:40,600
niman kemaj okinots on novio,

27
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,480
niman okijlij:

28
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:49,400
—Nochi tlakatl achtoj kitemaka on más uelik vino niman ijkuak on tenotsaltin miyek yokonikej,

29
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:52,800
kinmakaj on vino yejuan xmás uelik.

30
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:58,680
Pero tejua yej otikejeu on más uelik vino para más sakin* tiktemaka.

31
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:02,020
Yejua in tlen Jesús okichiu ne Caná de Galilea,

32
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:06,440
yejua iachtoj milagro yejuan okiteititij iueyilis,

33
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:10,880
niman on inomachtijkauan* okineltokakej.

34
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,720
Ijkuak ijkon yonochiu,

35
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,680
Jesús iuan inanaj,

36
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:22,500
ikniuan niman inomachtijkauan* oyajkej ipan on kalpan itoka Capernaúm kampa onenkej keski tonajli.

